of%20Babri%20Mosque.%20The%20temple%20has%20been%20built%20and%20is%20ready%20for%20inauguration%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20its%20mother%20organisation%20Rashtriyaswayam%20Sevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20are%20using%20the%20occasion%20to%20create%20a%20countrywide%20hysteria%20to%20demolish%20every%20shred%20of%20secularism%2C%20to%20have%20fuller%20control%20over%20temples%20of%20the%20country%2C%20to%20tighten%20authoritarian%20control%20over%20power%20and%20strengthen%20corporate%20control%20over%20the%20economy.%20The%20elite%2C%20including%20non-resident%20Indians%20(NRIs)%2C%20are%20exalted%2C%20feeling%20a%20sense%20of%20victory.%20The%20freedom%20in%201947%20did%20not%20please%20them%20as%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20preserve%20their%20privileged%20status.%20Religion%20implies%20truth.%20The%20shrine%20campaign%20has%20been%20a%20total%20negation%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-ram-temple-at-ayodhya-is-a-symbol-of-injustice-congress-leaders-should-stay-away-from-it%5C%22%3EThe%20Ram%20Temple%20at%20Ayodhya%20is%20a%20Symbol%20of%20Injustice%2C%20Congress%20Leaders%20Should%20Stay%20Away%20from%20It%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComposite%20culture%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%203%2C000%20years%2C%20religion%20remained%20eclipsed%20by%20untouchability%20and%20oppression%20of%20women.%20Temples%20did%20not%20allow%20entry%20of%20those%20who%20built%20them.%20The%20working%20classes%2C%20however%2C%20devised%20ways%20to%20worship%20the%20Almighty%20through%20tiny%20stones%20placed%20underneath%20trees%20and%20living%20a%20truthful%20life.%20Buddha%2C%202500%20years%20ago%2C%20evolved%20a%20religion%20beyond%20the%20confines%20of%20shrines%2C%20treating%20all%20human%20beings%20as%20equal.%20It%20appealed%20to%20large%20sections%20of%20society%20and%20prevailed%20for%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Middle%20Ages%20began%20the%20retreat%20when%20the%20hierarchal%20shrine-based%20religion%20reasserted%20itself.%20In%20the%2012th%20century%20began%20Bhakti%20and%20Sufi%20movements%20that%20defied%20all%20segregation%20and%20brought%20religion%20to%20the%20doorstep%20of%20the%20masses.%20Great%20spiritual%20figures%2C%20Sufis%20and%20saints%2C%20emerged%20from%20all%20communities%2C%20including%20the%20lower%20castes%2C%20marginalised%20sections%2C%20and%20women.%20It%20brought%20synthesis%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20Islam%2C%20and%20other%20religions%20and%20the%20process%20continued%20for%20centuries.%20It%20laid%20emphasis%20on%20truthful%20conduct%2C%20compassionate%20behaviour%2C%20and%20honest%20earnings.%20It%20built%20a%20strong%20composite%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EColonial%20phase%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20rulers%20in%20India%20re-organised%20the%20ruling%20hierarchy%20and%20created%20a%20class%20of%20landlords%2C%20moneylenders%2C%20and%20officers%20that%20was%20ruthless%20to%20the%20masses.%20Again%2C%20hierarchical%20and%20shrine-based%20religion%20became%20dominant%20and%20caste%20oppression%20became%20severe.%20In%20the%2019%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%20century%2C%20Jotiba%20Phule%2C%20Savitri%20Bai%20Phule%2C%20and%20others%20created%20a%20stir%20against%20it.%20Starting%20from%201916%20onwards%2C%20the%20eradication%20of%20untouchability%20became%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement.%20Satyagraha%20and%20Noncooperation%20movements%20posed%20a%20serious%20challenge%20to%20colonial%20rule.%20The%20native%20elite%20advanced%20communalism%20(organised%20religious%20hatred)%20as%20an%20instrument%20to%20sabotage%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%20They%20could%20not%20stop%20freedom%20but%20succeeded%20in%20creating%20a%20blood%20bath%20in%201946-47%20that%20led%20to%20partition%2C%20killing%20one%20million%20people%2C%20and%20rendering%2010%20million%20to%20cross%20the%