%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%2C%20I%20don't%20regret%20moving%20to%20Bermuda.%20The%20lifestyle%20experience%20I%20gained%20was%20invaluable.%C2%A0I%20lived%20in%20Bermuda%20for%2013%20years%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20US%20afterward.%20With%20this%20huge%20life%20lesson%20behind%20me%2C%20here's%20what%20I%20learned%20from%20my%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20I%20should've%20evaluated%20how%20a%20relocation%20would%20affect%20my%20financial%20goals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20financial%20coach%2C%20I%20now%20see%20that%20I%20seriously%20overlooked%20the%20impact%20such%20a%20move%20would%20have%20on%20my%20personal%20finances.%20My%20career%20was%20set%20back%20when%20I%20stopped%20working%20in%20commercial%20real%20estate%20for%20the%20move%20to%20Bermuda.%20This%20hurt%20my%20ability%20to%20earn%20an%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20marrying%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-to-deal-with-homesickness-loneliness-living-abroad-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20living%20overseas%3C%2Fa%3E%20allowed%20us%20to%20save%20money%20since%20my%20husband's%20employer%20paid%20for%20many%20expenses%20that%20we%20would've%20had%20to%20pay%20if%20we%20lived%20in%20the%20US.%20This%20helped%20us%20reach%20our%20financial%20goals%20sooner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20I%20wish%20I%20would've%20assessed%20if%20I'd%20be%20able%20to%20continue%20doing%20the%20things%20I%20loved%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20the%20outdoor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frelaxing-vacation-in-bermuda-2013-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eactivities%20I%20could%20do%20in%20Bermuda%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20scuba%20diving%2C%20snorkeling%2C%20riding%20my%20bike%2C%20and%20golfing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20normal%20Sunday%20afternoon%20activity%20was%20snorkeling%20with%20my%20family%20from%20our%20boat%20in%20one%20of%20the%20most%20beautiful%20places%20in%20the%20world.%20This%20was%20beyond%20spectacular%2C%20but%20I%20also%20love%20working.%20I%20didn't%20realize%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20work%20in%20real%20estate%20as%20a%20foreigner%20living%20in%20Bermuda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20lived%20in%20Bermuda%2C%20the%20general%20rule%20has%20been%20the%20same.%20The%20government%20of%20Bermuda%20states%20that%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.bm%2Fonline-services%2Fapplying-real-estate-broker-and-agent-licence%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20foreigners%20cannot%20work%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20Bermudian%20can%20do%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20foreigners%20to%20work%20in%20fields%20such%20as%20real%20estate.%20If%20you%20aren't%20a%20Bermudian%2C%20you%20must%20get%20permission%20from%20the%20minister%20responsible%20for%20immigration%20before%20you%20can%20work%20in%20Bermuda%20as%20a%20real%20estate%20broker%20or%20agent.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20good%20work%20opportunities%20available%20to%20me%20were%20in%20accounting%20or%20finance.%20I'd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-an-accountant-does-all-day-2014-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworked%20as%20an%20accountant%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20my%20move%20to%20real%20estate%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20work%20as%20an%20accountant%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20lost%20not%20working%20in%20Bermuda.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20I%20should've%20held%20rental%20properties%20in%20the%20US%20to%20accumulate%20real%20estate%20equity%20while%20living%20elsewhere.%20Extremely%20early%20retirement%20was%20hard%20for%20me%2C%20even%20in%20a%20beautiful%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20I'd%20always%20been%20interested%20in%20stocks%20and%20bonds%2C%20so%20handling%20our%20investments%20became%20my%20unpaid%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20It%20would've%20been%20smarter%20to%20decide%20if%20we%20wanted%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20same%20home%20for%20at%20least%20a%20decade%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChanging%20homes%20is%20a%20big%20element%20in%20moving.%20Homes%20become%20emotional%20anchors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.regobermuda.com%2Fbermuda-land-policy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ealmost%20impossible%20to%20purchase%20a%20home%20in%20Bermuda%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20foreigner.%20This%20led%20to%20my%20family%20renting%20three%20different%20homes%20while%20we%20lived%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%20in%20Bermuda%2C%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20when%20you%20rent%20a%20home%20you%20can%20only%20stay%20as%20long%20as%20the%20landlord%20allows.%20The%20owners%20of%20the%20first%20house%20we%20leased%20wanted%20to%20move%20into%20the%20home%20themselves%2C%20after%20a%20while.%20The%20second%20home%20only%20had%20two%20bedrooms%20and%20we%20wanted%20three%20bedrooms%20since%20our%20family%20had%20grown%20and%20we%20had%20frequent%20guests%2C%20so%20we%20moved%20again.%C2%A0I%20prefer%20owning%20my%20home%20and%20moving%20less%20frequently%2C%20so%20I%20wish%20I'd%20considered%20this%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20I%20failed%20to%20consider%20the%20long-term%20social%20aspects%20of%20an%20international%20move%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20merits%20to%20the%20old%20saying%20bloom%20where%20you're%20planted.%20I%20lean%20toward%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fintrovert-vs-extrovert%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeing%20an%20introvert%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Living%20abroad%20among%20an%20international%20community%20was%20a%20wonderful%20experience%20in%20many%20ways%20but%20it%20wasn't%20easy%20from%20a%20social%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFriends%20who%20weren't%20Bermudians%20moved%20after%20solid%20friendships%20were%20formed.%20I%20didn't%20have%20difficulty%20making%20Bermudian%20friends%2C%20but%20they%20already%20had%20a%20network%20of%20their%20own%20local%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20and%20I%20was%20a%20temporary%20resident%20which%20created%20some%20challenges.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20finally%20left%20the%20island%2C%20we%20moved%20to%20Austin%20where%20I%20knew%20no%20one.%20I%20was%20in%20the%20fourth%20location%20for%20making%20new%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20I%20didn't%20take%20enough%20time%20to%20discern%20whether%20such%20a%20move%20would%20fit%20into%20my%20life%20goals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20participated%20in%20a%20time%20management%20course%20a%20few%20months%20before%20the%20option%20to%20move%20to%20Bermuda%20presented%20itself.%20One%20of%20my%20biggest%20goals%20was%20to%20live%20on%20the%20water.%20I%20envisioned%20this%20happening%20decades%20later%2C%20but%20I%20achieved%20it%20in%20my%20late%2020s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20spectacular%2C%20but%20due%20to%20this%20decision%2C%20I%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-a-plan-for-your-goals-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20life%20goals%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20weren't%20reached%20%E2%80%94%20like%20a%20long-term%20career%20in%20commercial%20real%20estate%20with%20the%20leading%20retail%20brokerage%20firm%20in%20Houston.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20realize%20how%20much%20this%20move%20would%20steer%20my%20life%20because%20I%20was%20young.%20That%20direction%20was%20based%20on%20someone%20else's%20career%2C%20not%20my%20own.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20this%20was%20a%20challenge%20for%20me%20being%20a%20very%20independent%20woman%2C%20so%20I%20wish%20I'd%20known%20that%20before%20I%20moved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELiving%20in%20Bermuda%20was%20night%20and%20day%20from%20living%20in%20Houston%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHouston%20is%20a%20large%20city%2C%20while%20Bermuda%20is%20an%20island%20just%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FBermuda%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520territory%2520consists%2520of%2520181%2Cmetres%2520tall%2520