ompanies%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Cushman%20%26amp%3B%20Wakefield%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20doing%20already%2C%20Companieh%20said.%20This%20includes%20creating%20partnerships%2C%20reviewing%20commercial%20terms%2C%20beefing%20up%20cybersecurity%20teams%2C%20and%20hiring%20and%20training%20talent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20very%20personal%20to%20every%20single%20organization.%20The%20journey%20you%20go%20on%20is%20very%20individualized%20to%20your%20organization.%20And%20we're%20doing%20right%20by%20ours%20by%20being%20authentic%20to%20who%20we%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELinkedIn%3A%20Dan%20Shapero%2C%20chief%20technology%20officer%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dan%20Shapero%2C%20LinkedIn%20COO%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656f6d4c58e7c0c29a29cd6f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDan%20Shapero.%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20LinkedIn%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20rewrite%20its%20roadmap%20to%20incorporate%20AI%20across%20a%20range%20of%20capabilities%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-dan-shapero-interview-2024-outlook-amazed-by-ai-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EDan%20Shapero%2C%20chief%20technology%20officer%2C%20told%20BI%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20lucky%20enough%20to%20see%20some%20of%20the%20next-gen%20AI%20models%20by%20being%20part%20of%20Microsoft%20in%20the%20middle%20of%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20networking%20platform%20knew%20this%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Btime%20of%20massive%20experimentation%20to%20see%20where%20AI%20made%20the%20biggest%20difference%26quot%3B%20for%20both%20recruiters%20and%20job%20seekers.%20He%20said%20the%20company%20will%20use%20AI%20to%20help%20people%20write%20their%20profiles%20because%20people%20can%20find%20it%20awkw