20officer%2C%20told%20BI%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20develop%20a%20method%20that%20you%20can%20combine%20the%20strength%20of%20a%20large%20language%20model%20with%20all%20the%20real-time%2C%20company-specific%20information%20that%20you%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20German%20company%20%E2%80%94%20which%20focuses%20on%20cloud-based%20subscription%20services%20for%20its%20financial-reporting%2C%20inventory-tracking%2C%20and%20human-resources%20applications%20%E2%80%94%20looks%20at%20the%20processes%20of%20companies%2C%20including%20financials%2C%20procurements%2C%20HR%2C%20customer%20relations%2C%20or%20the%20supply%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESAP%20has%20worked%20within%20the%20machine-learning%20AI%20space%20for%20almost%20nine%20years.%20The%20company%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20answer%20questions%20around%20how%20to%20work%20with%20data%3B%20how%20to%20protect%20data%3B%20how%20to%20use%20data%20ethically%3B%20what%20tools%20data%20scientists%20need%3B%20%26quot%3Band%20how%20can%20we%20rethink%20and%20upgrade%20to%20generative%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20R%26amp%3BD%20SAP%20invested%20in%20business%20AI%20paid%20off%2C%20Mueller%20said.%20%26quot%3BOver%2025%2C000%20SAP%20Cloud%20customers%20using%20at%20least%20one%20of%20our%20130%20AI%20scenarios.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20there%20are%20still%20concerns.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20risk%20is%20not%20that%20there's%20new%20technology.%20The%20risk%20is%20that%20we%20don't%20lean%20in%20and%20don't%20invest%20the%20extra%20time%2C%20extra%20hours.%20Because%20it%20needs%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20time%3B%20it%20is%20a%20little%20complex%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20needs%20to%20lean%20in%2C%20learn.%20That%2C%20I%20think%2C%20is%20the%20largest%20risk.%20Then%20you%20have%20divergence%20in%20society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EServiceNow%3A%20Chris%20Bedi%2C%20chief%20digital%20information%20officer%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chris%20Bedi%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6578a12d7a3c8094d5dc203c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChris%20Bedi.%3Cp%3EServiceNow%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EServiceNow%20wants%20to%20become%20an%20%26quot%3BAI-first%26quot%3B%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fservicenow-chief-digital-information-officer-2024-ai-innovation-fun-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EChris%20Bedi%2C%20chief%20digital%20information%20officer%2C%20told%20BI%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20we're%20early%20innings%2C%20especially%20with%20gen%20AI%2C%20but%20we%20are%20pushing%20on%20it%20hard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EServiceNow%2C%20which%20provides%20a%20cloud-based%20platform%20for%20automating%20IT%20workflows%2C%20uses%20generative%20AI%20search%20for%20employees%20and%20customers.%20Generative%20AI%20also%20enables%20work%20to%20get%20done%20faster%2C%20like%20reading%20and%20interpreting%20information.%20%26quot%3BLiterally%20you%20run%20a%20process%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20hours.%20It's%20additive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20part%20of%20understanding%20and%20integrating%20AI%20is%20training%20the%20company's%2022%2C000%20employees.%20ServiceNow%20recently%20held%20an%20AI%20learning%20day%20that%20included%20panels%20to%20help%20demystify%20the%20technology%2C%20Bedi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeams%20involved%20in%20information%20technology%2C%20human%20resources%2C%20and%20customer%20support%20don't%20feel%20threatened%20by%20gen%20AI%2C%20he%20said.%20About%2064%25%20believe%20it's%20helping%20boost%20productivity%2C%20according%20to%20Bedi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EServiceNow%20also%20considers%20what%20happens%20when%20AI%20takes%20on%20a%20bigger%20part%20of%20someone's%20job.%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20we%20fill%20in%20the%20gaps%20of%20time%20to%