.com%2Fminute-long-workouts-may-help-prevent-early-death-study-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E10%20minutes%20a%20day%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20your%20talent%20and%20the%20benefits%20will%20creep%20up%20on%20you.%20You%20don't%20have%20to%20be%20smashing%20exercise%20out%20for%20two%20or%20three%20hours%20a%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20took%20me%20ages%20to%20get%20to%205k%2C%20but%20by%20doing%2010%20minutes%20a%20day%2C%20my%20fitness%20has%20really%20maintained%20itself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESee%20the%20run%20as%20self%20care%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20never%20that%20difficult%20to%20prioritize%20myself%20for%2010%20minutes%20a%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Sachdev%20said.%20She%20said%20that%20getting%20herself%20out%20and%20on%20a%20run%20hasn't%20ever%20been%20hard%2C%20because%20she%20sees%20it%20as%20a%20privilege%20that%20she%20has%20that%20time%20and%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20frames%20it%20as%20a%20choice%3A%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I'm%20just%20at%20home%2C%20it's%20a%20choice%20between%20scrolling%20on%20my%20phone%20for%2010%20minutes%20or%20getting%20outside%20for%2010%20minutes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20decided%20to%20make%20the%20choice%20to%20run%20for%2010%20minutes%20as%20a%20commitment%20to%20herself%20and%20her%20health%2C%20and%20because%20she%20also%20sees%20running%20as%20a%20way%20to%20protect%20her%20time%2C%20since%20it%20can%20be%20an%20excuse%20to%20say%20no%20to%20things%20she%20didn't%20want%20to%20do%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGo%20slowly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESachdev%20said%20she%20didn't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fsigns-running-too-much-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epush%20herself%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20run%20too%20fast%2C%20and%20that%20the%20right%20pace%20is%20one%20at%20which%20you%20can%20still%20talk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20a%20video%20she%20saw%20of%20a%20man%20bouncing%20a%20tennis%20ball%20on%20a%20jog%20was%20a%20