ure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Clumps%20of%20parmesan%20on%20Wingstop's%20garlic%20wings.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581d698cefc010bea25015d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20didn't%20like%20the%20clumps%20of%20Parmesan%20on%20Wingstop's%20garlic%20wings.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Parmesan%20cheese%20was%20clearly%20dusted%20on%20top%20of%20the%20wing%20with%20a%20shaker.%20At%20Popeyes%2C%20the%20cheese%20was%20part%20of%20the%20sauce%2C%20so%20you%20could%20taste%20it%20with%20every%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wingstop%20wing%20doesn't%20have%20thick%20breading%2C%20so%20it%20had%20no%20crunchy%20texture%20like%20Popeyes.%20The%20clumpy%20grated%20cheese%20barely%20clings%20to%20the%20wing.%20Half%20of%20the%20Wingstop%20grated%20cheese%20fell%20to%20the%20table%20or%20on%20my%20shirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinner%3A%20Popeyes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Honey%20BBQ%20wings%20at%20Popeyes%20were%20sticky%2C%20but%20finger-licking%20good.%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221623%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Honey%20BBQ%20Wings%20at%20Popeyes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581c5f0a79e5746976af2d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221217%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Honey%20BBQ%20wings%20at%20Popeyes%20are%20tossed%20in%20a%20sweet%20and%20tangy%20sauce.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Honey%20BBQ%20wings%20at%20Popeyes%20are%20tossed%20in%20a%20sauce%20made%20with%20a%20mix%20of%20tamarind%2C%20sweet%20honey%2C%20and%20molasses.%20The%20honey%20made%20these%20wings%20a%20sticky%20mess.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tamarind%20and%20honey%20gave%20this%20barbecue%20sauce%20a%20creative%20kick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20liked%20the%20innovation%20here.%20It%20wasn't%20a%20boring%20barbecue%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWingstop's%20barbecue%20wings%20were%20plain%2C%20but%20delicious.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wingstop's%20Hickory%20Smoked%20BBQ%20wings%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581c595cefc010bea24f0bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Hickory%20Smoked%20BBQ%20wings%20at%20Wingstop%20were%20mighty%20sticky.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wingstop%20wings%20came%20slathered%20in%20tangy%20sweet%20barbecue%20sauce%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20smoky%20flavor.%20I%20love%20smoky-flavored%20food%2C%20so%20these%20wings%20were%20pleasing%20to%20my%20palate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20Wingstop%20chicken%20wings%20are%20much%20smaller%20with%20less%20meat%20compared%20to%20Popeyes.%20I'm%20also%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20Wingstop's%20thinly%20coated%20breading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinner%3A%20It%20was%20close%2C%20but%20Popeyes%20won%20this%20round.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPopeyes%20said%20the%20Sweet%20'N%20Spicy%20wings%2C%20tested%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20are%20the%20chain's%20%26quot%3Bbest%20performing%20product%20since%20the%20infamous%20Chicken%20Sandwich.%26quot%3B%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Popeyes%20Sweet%20'N%20Spicy%20wings%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cbb2f7a3c8094d5ddb4fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sweet%20'N%20Spicy%20wings%20are%20swimming%20in%20chili%20oil.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20statement%20speaks%20volumes%2C%20as%20the%20chain's%20chicken%20sandwich%20sparked%20a%20chicken%20sandwich%20war%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-it-costs-to-open-a-chick-fil-a-20