It%20was%20nearly%20identical%20in%20taste%20to%20Popeyes'%20Sweet%20'N%20Spicy%20wings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Popeyes%20Sweet%20'N%20Spicy%20wing%20had%20more%20heat%20and%20bolder%20flavors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWinner%3A%20Popeyes.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20next%20matchup%20pits%20the%20not-so-hot%20Ghost%20Pepper%20wings%20at%20Popeyes%20against%20Wingstop's%20Louisiana%20Rub%20wings.%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Popeyes%20ghost%20pepper%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cace00ec98e92f7501d42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere's%20no%20real%20heat%20in%20the%20Ghost%20Pepper%20wings.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBelieve%20it%20or%20not%2C%20the%20Ghost%20Pepper%20wings%20at%20Popeyes%20were%20not%20hot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20not%20tossed%20in%20any%20sauce.%20The%20heat%20comes%20from%20marinating%20the%20chicken%20for%2012%20hours%20in%20ghost%20pepper%20spices.%20It's%20the%20least%20spicy%20of%20the%20five%20Popeyes%20chicken%20wings.%20They%20were%20a%20big%20letdown%2C%20as%20I%20prepared%20my%20palate%20for%20some%20scorching%20heat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Louisiana%20Rub%20wings%20at%20Wingstop%20were%20lightly%20coated%20in%20a%20Cajun%20seasoning.%20They%20were%20the%20best%20wings%20I%20tried%20at%20Wingstop.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wingstop-Louisiana%20Rub.jpeg%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6581c985cefc010bea24f6d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWingstop's%20Louisiana%20Rub%20wings%20were%20the%20best%20of%20the%20four%20we%20tasted.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Louisiana%20Rub%20wings%20had%20the%20perfect%20amount%20of%20heat.%20The%20se