um%2Farticle67680883.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20Department%20of%20Tourism%20announced%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20War%20Art%20Museum%20across%20136%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Gorai%20in%20June%20last%20year.%20A%20budget%20of%20Rs%2050%20crore%20was%20set%20aside%20for%20the%20project.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20boundary%20wall%20of%20the%20museum%20has%20been%20constructed%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%20has%20already%20led%20to%20the%20demolition%20of%20some%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20Shivaji%20museum%20project%20was%20announced%20%5Bin%20mid-2023%5D%2C%20there%20have%20been%20several%20visits%20by%20Maharashtra%20Tourism%20Development%20Corporation%20(MTDC)%20staff%20along%20with%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kusum%20Kisan%20Babar%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Gorai%E2%80%99s%20Babar%20Pada%20tribal%20hamlet%2C%20told%20the%20newspaper.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20the%20constant%20fear%20of%20losing%20the%20land%20my%20ancestors%20left%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20says%20that%20the%20land%20set%20aside%20for%20the%20project%20has%20been%20with%20them%20for%20generations%2C%20and%20they%20are%20dependent%20on%20it.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20no%20objection%20to%20the%20museum%2C%20but%20it%20should%20not%20be%20built%20on%20our%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20Asmita%20Kolekar%20from%20Birsa%20Munda%20Pada%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20is%20reportedly%20in%20the%20process%20of%20filing%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20against%20the%20takeover%20of%20their%20land.%20Earlier%20in%202011%2C%20the%20same%20court%20had%20rejected%20MTDC%E2%80%99s%20tourism%20proposal%20to%20construct%20hotels%20and%20resorts%20in%20and%20around%20Gorai%20and%20Manori%20villages%2C%20as%20these%20areas%20are%20ecologically%20sensitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajendra%20Bhosale%2C%20collector%2C%20Mumbai%20Suburban%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20tribal%20communities%20are%20practising%20agriculture%20on%20sanctioned%20land%2C%20they%20will%20not%20be%20displaced%20or%20affected%20by%20such%20projects.%20%E2%80%A6Even%20if%20that%20particular%20place%20is%20affected%2C%20they%20will%20be%20rehabilitated%20safely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20when%20the%20project%20was%20announced%2C%20Maharashtra%20tourism%20minister%20Mangal%20Prabhat%20Lodha%20had%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cencroachments%E2%80%9D%20on%20government%20land%20were%20being%20removed.%20%E2%80%9CEncroachment%20on%20the%20site%20of%20Maharashtra%20Tourism%20Development%20Corporation%20in%20Gorai%20has%20been%20removed%20today.%20A%20war%20museum%20will%20be%20set%20up%20at%20the%20plot%20where%20the%20war%20skills%20and%20armor%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20will%20be%20displayed%20so%20that%20future%20generations%20can%20experience%20the%20glorious%20history%20of%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20and%20take%20inspiration%20from%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fmumbai%2Fshivaji-war-memorial-will-come-up-in-gorai-minister-8649360%2F%5C%22%3Ehe%20said%20in%20June%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704187944000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F08%2F7915351394_a8eeecfb5d_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwarli-tribe-in-suburban-mumbai-fear-displacement-due-to-shivaji-museum-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Maharashtra%20Department%20of%20Tourism%20announced%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20War%20Art%20Museum%20across%20136%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20Gorai%20in%20June%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwarli-tribe-in-suburban-mumbai-fe