%22%3A%22In%20Row%20Over%20Vice%20Chancellor%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Arrest%20And%20Bail%20At%20Midnight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20dramatic%20late%20night%20arrest%20of%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Periyar%20University%20last%20week%20has%20triggered%20a%20huge%20political%20controversy%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu's%20opposition%20BJP%20alleges%20that%20Vice%20Chancellor%20R%20Jagannathan%20was%20arrested%20over%20concocted%20charges%20for%20refusing%20to%20appoint%20candidates%20pushed%20by%20the%20state%20government's%20Higher%20Education%20Department%20for%20the%20posts%20of%20Registrar%20and%20Controller%20of%20Examinations%20for%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jagannathan%20was%20%26quot%3Bpunished%26quot%3B%20for%20following%20rules%2C%20alleged%20P%20Kanagasabapathy%2C%20Vice%20President%20of%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20BJP.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20Professor%20Jagannathan%20for%20many%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kanagasabapathy%2C%20a%20retired%20professor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20my%20senior%20and%20a%20very%20strict%20and%20honest%20person.%20For%20too%20many%20decades%2C%20unfit%20persons%20have%20been%20appointed%20to%20important%20posts%20in%20universities%20thanks%20to%20political%20interference%20and%20corruption.%20Because%20Professor%20Jagannathan%20tried%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20system%2C%20he%20has%20been%20punished.%20Let%20a%20fair%20enquiry%20take%20place%20-%20if%20he%20has%20indeed%20done%20what%20has%20been%20alleged%20against%20him%2C%20let%20him%20be%20punished%20according%20to%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Midnight%20Arrest%20%26amp%3B%20Bail%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2026%2C%20Dr%20Jagannathan%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Salem%20police%20and%20produced%20before%20a%20Judicial%20Magistrate%20at%2011.45%20p.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%2C%20filed%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20lawyer%20Isaiah%20Elangovan%2C%20includes%20charges%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Prevention%20of%20Atrocities%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20claims%20I%20Elangovan%20had%20uncovered%20irregularities%20and%20corruption%20in%20the%20functioning%20of%20Periyar%20University%2C%20and%20when%20he%20confronted%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%2C%20he%20was%20subjected%20to%20caste%20slurs%20and%20threats%20to%20his%20life.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20the%20corruption%20claim%2C%20the%20FIR%20says%20the%20Periyar%20University%20Technology%20Entrepreneurship%20and%20Research%20Foundation%20(PUTER%20Foundation)%20and%20PUTER%20Park%20Lab%20were%20set%20up%20without%20proper%20approvals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20midnight%20hearing%2C%20the%20magistrate%20was%20not%20convinced%20by%20the%20arrest%20made%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Atrocities%20against%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Magistrate%20found%20the%20Investigation%20Officer's%20details%20%26quot%3Bvery%20meagre%20and%20skeletal.%26quot%3B%20The%20complaint%2C%20he%20noted%2C%20did%20not%20show%20any%20%26quot%3Bactual%20charge%20of%20misappropriation%20or%20cheating%20against%20the%20accused.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Magistrate%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20reasons%20best%20known%20to%20him%2C%20the%20Investigation%20officer%20directly%20resorted%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20accused%20and%20also%20produced%20him%20before%20this%20court%20within%20four%20hours%20of%20his%20arrest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecution%20argued%20against%20Dr%20Jagannathan's%20bail%2C%20saying%20the%20complainant%20was%20not%20present.%20The%20Magistrate%20did%20not%20deem%20that%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vice%20Chancellor%20was%20released%20on%20own%20bail%2C%20which%20means%20he%20could%20sign%20his%20own%20bail%20bond%2C%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20he%20would%20bring%20two%20bonds%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20each%20the%20next%20day.%20The%20hearing%20ended%20at%203%20am%20on%20December%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Complainant's%20Version%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Elangovan%2C%20explaining%20his%20absence%20at%20the%20hearing%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20I%20know%20that%20the%20accused%20will%20be%20produced%20before%20the%20Magistrate%20at%20that%20time%3F%20The%20Magistrate%20must%20issue%20notice%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20a%20sessions%20judge%20should%20have%20presided%20over%20the%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20challenged%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor's%20bail%20in%20the%20Madras%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20fight%20it%20tooth%20and%20nail%20-%20he%20(Dr%20Jagannathan)%20has%20duped%20the%20government%20and%20the%20University.%20He%20has%20usurped%20the%20entire%20syndicate%20and%20is%20running%20the%20University%20as%20if%20he%20is%20a%20feudal%20lord.%20He%20refused%20to%20meet%20with%20me%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20get%20out.%20He%20called%20me%20by%20my%20caste%20name.%20I%20am%20a%20practising%20advocate%20and%20I%20will%20not%20make%20a%20mistake%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Elangovan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20six%20years%2C%20I%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20District%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Welfare%20Committee%20constituted%20by%20the%20District%20Collector%2C%20Vellore.%20I%20am%20not%20a%20member%20of%20any%20political%20party%20and%20I%20cannot%20play%20second%20fiddle%20to%20any%20political%20party.%20These%20allegations%20of%20political%20interference%20are%20a%20story%20built%20by%20the%20supporters%20of%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20insisted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Turbulent%20Syndicate%20Meeting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20reached%20out%20to%20members%20of%20the%20Periyar%20University%20Syndicate%3B%20they%20spoke%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%20and%20claimed%20they%20feared%20harsh%20reprisal%20from%20the%20state%20government%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFriction%20between%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%2C%20government%20officials%20and%20the%20Periyar%20University%20Employees%20Union%2C%20a%20union%20of%20non-teaching%20staff%2C%20peaked%20in%20November%20over%20the%20sacking%20of%20four%20employees%20over%20insubordination%20and%20financial%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sacked%20employees%20had%20gone%20to%20court%2C%20which%20had%20recommended%20that%20the%20University%20form%20a%20committee%20to%20%26quot%3Bconsider%26quot%3B%20their%20request%20for%20reinstatement.%20But%20the%20decision%20was%20not%20reversed.%20This%20raised%20strong%20objections%20from%20state%20Minister%20KN%20Nehru%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20DMK's%20party%20in-charge%20for%20Salem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnesses%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20minister%20had%20slammed%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%20in%20early%20November%20for%20terminating%20the%20four%20employees%2C%20who%20had%20allegedly%20been%20recommended%20by%20him.%20When%20Dr%20Jagannathan%20cited%20the%20rules%2C%20the%20minister%20allegedly%20shouted%20at%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Minister's%20displeasure%20is%20evident%20in%20an%20interview%20given%20by%20him%20to%20Tamil%20news%20channel%20Thanthi%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20University%20in%20which%20four%20people%20have%20been%20dismissed%20despite%20the%20court%20asking%20the%20University%20to%20reinstate%20them.%20The%20Vice%20Chancellor%20is%20refusing%20to%20take%20them%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nehru%20told%20the%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20the%20reason%20-%20he%20just%20says%20he%20cannot%20reinstate%20them...%20I%20will%20say%20confidently%20that%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%20in%20Salem%20terminated%20four%20employees%20for%20being%20DMK%20members%20and%20despite%20the%20court%20ordering%20the%20university%20to%20reinstate%20them%20and%20despite%20multiple%20pleas%20by%20the%20staff%2C%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%20has%20refused.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20was%20asked%20whether%20there%20was%20interference%20by%20the%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20he%20is%20interfering%20or%20not%2C%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%20is%20afraid.%20He%20is%20worried%20that%20someone%20may%20get%20upset.%20This%20is%20a%20small%20matter%3B%20the%20Governor%20may%20not%20speak%20about%20this.%20But%20the%20Vice%20Chancellor%20is%20using%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Nehru%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2019%2C%20two%20days%20before%20a%20syndicate%20meeting%2C%20Elangovan%20sent%20emails%20to%20members%20of%20the%20syndicate%20as%20well%20as%20government%20officials%20alleging%20corruption.%20The%20Vice%20Chancellor%20has%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%20seeking%20a%20probe%20into%20confidential%20meeting%20agenda%20being%20leaked%20to%20Elangovan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20meeting%20on%20November%2021%2C%20a%20Deputy%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Higher%20Education%20Department%20arrived%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20department's%20Secretary%2C%20A%20Karthik%2C%20who%20is%20a%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20witness%2C%20Mr%20Karthik%20then%20joined%20the%20meeting%20through%20video%20conference%20and%20asked%20that%20a%20sealed%20cover%20be%20opened%20for%20the%20list%20of%20names%20for%20Registrar%20and%20Controller%20of%20Examinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Vice%20Chancellor%20insisted%20that%20rules%20must%20be%20followed%20and%20that%20meritorious%20candidates%20should%20be%20selected%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20witness.%20%26quot%3BAn%20exchange%20of%20words%20took%20place%2C%20and%20the%20VC%20asked%20the%20Secretary%20why%20he%20was%20joining%20via%20video%20conference%20when%20a%20Deputy%20Secretary%20was%20already%20present.%20He%20said%20the%20rules%20do%20not%20permit%20it%20and%20the%20