t%3B%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Panamanian%20flag%20carrier%20Copa%20Airlines%20had%20higher%20on-time%20performance%20than%20Avianca%20at%2089.46%25%2C%20making%20it%20the%20most%20punctual%20airline%20in%20Latin%20America.%20However%2C%20it%20doesn't%20meet%20the%20regional%20requirement%20of%20flying%20to%20at%20least%20three%20regions%20daily%20to%20qualify%20as%20a%20global%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20firmly%20believe%20that%20a%20straight%20ranking%20without%20these%20considerations%20would%20not%20be%20useful%2C%20and%20that's%20due%20to%20the%20very%20different%20sizes%20and%20operating%20models%20of%20the%20world's%20airlines%2C%26quot%3B%20Bowen%20told%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20naming%20the%20world's%20most%20punctual%20global%20airline%2C%20Cirium%20also%20hands%20out%20the%20%26quot%3Bplatinum%20award%26quot%3B%20to%20what%20Bowen%20described%20as%20the%20best%20all-around%20global%20airline%20for%20%26quot%3Boperational%20excellence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-and-worst-airlines-for-delays-cancellations-2022-delta-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewinner%20is%20Delta%20Air%20Lines%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20time.%20The%20company%20was%20also%20named%20the%20fourth%20most%20on-time%20airline%20among%20global%20carriers%20and%20the%20most%20on-time%20airline%20in%20North%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bowen%2C%20Cirium%20not%20only%20based%20its%20winner%20on%20punctuality%20but%20also%20the%20%26quot%3Bcomplexity%20of%20its%20operations%20and%20capacity%20to%20provide%20more%20benefit%20to%20passengers%20and%20airports.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECirium's%20other%202023%20winners%20were%20Spanish%20low-cost%20carrier%20Iberia%20Express%20in%20Europe%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflying-ana-the-room-business-class-new-york-japan-review-2023-4%23-and