%7B%22title%22%3A%22MK%20Stalin%20On%20Stage%2C%20PM's%20%26quot%3BNational%20Interest%26quot%3B%20Tribute%20To%20Captain%20Vijayakanth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20paid%20tribute%20to%20Desiya%20Murpokku%20Dravida%20Kazhagam%20(DMDK)%20founder%20and%20renowned%20actor%20Vijayakanth%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20'captain'%20not%20just%20in%20cinema%20but%20in%20politics%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20a%20few%20days%20ago%2C%20we%20lost%20Thiru%20Vijayakanth%20ji.%20He%20was%20a%20captain%20not%20only%20in%20the%20world%20of%20cinema%2C%20but%20also%20in%20politics.%20He%20won%20the%20hearts%20of%20people%20through%20his%20work%20in%20cinema.%20As%20a%20politician%2C%20he%20always%20put%20national%20interest%20above%20everything.%20I%20pay%20my%20tributes%20to%20him%20and%20express%20condolences%20to%20his%20family%20and%20admirers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Tiruchirapalli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20on%20a%20two-day%20visit%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20for%20a%20host%20of%20events.%20Today%2C%20he%20inaugurated%20and%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20for%20development%20projects%20worth%20nearly%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%20and%20opened%20the%20new%20terminal%20at%20Trichy%20airport.%20Earlier%2C%20he%20attended%20a%20convocation%20event%20at%20Bharathidasan%20University%20in%20Tiruchirapalli%20as%20chief%20guest.%20At%20both%20events%2C%20he%20shared%20stage%20with%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin.%20Mr%20Stalin%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20DMK%2C%20is%20a%20key%20face%20of%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%20that%20is%20gearing%20up%20to%20take%20on%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20tribute%20to%20Vijayakanth%2C%20who%20died%20on%20December%2028%20after%20battling%20a%20long%20illness%2C%20drew%20loud%20cheers.%C2%A0The%2071-year-old%20leader%2C%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20political%20landscape%2C%20got%20the%20title%20'Captain'%20for%20his%20role%20in%201991%20movie%20Captain%20Prabhakaran.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20floods%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20%26quot%3BThe%20last%20few%20weeks%20of%202023%20were%20difficult%20for%20many%20people%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20We%20lost%20many%20of%20our%20fellow%20citizens%20due%20to%20heavy%20rainfall.%20There%20has%20also%20been%20a%20significant%20loss%20of%20property.%20The%20central%20government%20stands%20with%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20this%20time%20of%20crisis.%20We%20are%20providing%20every%20possible%20support%20to%20the%20state%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20pay%20his%20respects%20to%20agricultural%20scientist%20Dr%20MS%20Swaminathan%2C%20who%20is%20considered%20the%20main%20architect%20of%20the%20green%20revolution%20that%20ensured%20India's%20food%20security.%20The%2098-year-old%20died%20this%20September.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20also%20remember%20another%20son%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Dr%20MS%20Swaminathan.%20He%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20ensuring%20food%20security%20for%20our%20country.%20We%20lost%20him%20last%20year%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704183420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fvlgd0ejg_modi-stalin-pti_625x300_02_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmk-stalin-pm-narendra-modi-vijayakanth-mk-stalin-on-dais-pms-national-interest-tribute-to-captain-vijayakanth-4785682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20paid%20tribute%20to%20Desiya%20Murpokku%20Dravida%20Kazhagam%20(DMDK)%20founder%20and%20renowned%20actor%20Vijayakanth%2C%20saying%20he%20was%20'captain'%20not%20just%20in%20the%20cinema%20but%20in%20politics%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3