t%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Ftrichy%2Fpm-narendra-modi-says-centre-stands-with-tamil-nadu-people-extends-all-possible-support-to-flood-hit-state%2Farticleshow%2F106480118.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRomanticism%20vs%20Realism%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar's%20Swipe%20At%20Nehrus%20China%20Approach%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEAM%20S%20Jaishankar%20has%20reiterated%20that%20India%20should%20deal%20with%20China%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20realism%20and%20asserted%20that%20the%20relationship%20should%20be%20based%20on%20the%20three%20mutual%20understandings-%20respect%2C%20sensitivity%2C%20and%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20reassessed%20India's%20approach%20of%20engaging%20with%20China%20with%20realism%20in%20order%20to%20checkmate%20its%20aggressive%20measures%2C%20while%20also%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20romanticism%20of%20the%20Nehruvian%20era%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20argue%20for%20dealing%20with%20China%20from%20a%20basis%20of%20realism%20--%20that%20strain%20of%20realism%2C%20which%20I%20feel%20--%20strains%20all%20the%20way%20from%20Sardar%20Patel%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%20--%20that%20is%20the%20strain%20of%20realism%20which%20I%20feel%20should%20allow%20us%20to%20have%20a%20certain%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Jaishankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20also%20lauded%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20his%20pragmatic%20approach%20on%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20that%20the%20Modi%20Government%20has%20been%20very%20much%20more%20and%20in%20conformity%20with%20a%20strain%20of%20realism%2C%20which%20originated%20from%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20EAM%20Dr%20S%20Jaishankar%20on%20Nehru%20Vs%20Sardar%20Patel's%20%E2%80%9Cattitude%E2%80%9D%20on%20China%20and%20what%20policy%20the%20Modi%20govt%20follows%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20talk%20about%20foreign%20policy%2C%20we've%20had%20a%20strain%20of%20realism%20and%20non-realism%20about%20China.%20It%20begins%20from%20day%20one%20where%20there%20is%20a%20sharp%20difference%20of%20opinion%20on%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FduYydJXgt9%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FduYydJXgt9%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1742058238915580399%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20difference%20in%20the%20approach%20of%20India's%20first%20Home%20Minister%20and%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Sardar%20Patel%20and%20first%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20Jaishankar%20highlighted%20the%20difference%20of%20opinion%20among%20the%20two%20stalwarts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20when%20it%20came%2C%20for%20example%20to%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20seat%2C%20it's%20not%20my%20case%20that%20we%20should%20have%20necessarily%20taken%20the%20seat%2C%20it's%20a%20different%20debate%2C%20but%20to%20say%20that%20we%20should%20first%20let%20China%20--%20China's%20interest%20should%20come%20first%2C%20it's%20a%20very%20peculiar%20statement%20to%20make%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20while%20dealing%20with%20the%20approach%20of%20Nehru%20and%20Sardar%20Patel's%20realism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20into%20Nehru's%20tenure%2C%20Sino-Indian%20relations%20were%20characterised%20by%20what%20was%20perceived%20as%20friendship%20and%20cordiality%20that%20covered%20both%20bilateral%20and%20regional%20and%20international%20issues%20however%2C%20India%20got%20a%20rude%20awakening%20when%20China%20launched%20a%20war%20in%201962%20that%20gave%20decision-makers%20in%20New%20Delhi%20a%20reality%20check%20on%20their%20China%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20two%20hands%20to%20clap.%20I%20pose%20the%20issue%20in%20this%20manner%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20last%2075%20plus%20years%20of%20our%20foreign%20policy%2C%20they%20have%20a%20strain%20of%20realism%20about%20China%20and%20have%20a%20strain%20of%20idealism%2C%20romanticism%2C%20non-realism.%20It%20begins%20right%20from%20day%20one%2C%20there%20is%20a%20sharp%20difference%20of%20opinion%20--%20how%20to%20respond%20to%20China%20between%20Nehru%20and%20Sardar%20Patel%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20while%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20the%20two%20nations%20will%20bury%20the%20hatchet%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20also%20dwelt%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BChindia%20policy%26quot%3B%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20alternative%20strain%20which%20starts%20from%20Nehru's%20China's%20first%20policy%20--%20first%20let%20China%20take%20seat%2C%20then%20we%20will%20see%20for%20India.%20From%20China's%20first%20policy%2C%20it%20ends%20up%20as%20Chindia%20policy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChindia%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20idea%20that%20projects%20the%20joint%20rise%20of%20China%20and%20India%20and%20was%20promoted%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20who%20called%20for%20constructive%20cooperation%20and%20competition%20between%20the%20Asian%20giants%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20should%20ask%20the%20inventor%20of%20the%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Jaishankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20the%20pivot%20India%20took%20on%20China%2C%20the%20union%20minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20believe%20it's%20a%20pivot%20we%20have%20taken%2C%20we%20have%20tried%20to%20construct%20a%20relationship%20which%20is%20based%2C%20as%20I%20say%20on%20three%20mutuals%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20is%2C%20unless%20that%20mutuality%20is%20recognised%20--%20this%20relationship%20will%20find%20very%20difficult%20to%20progress.%20Today%2C%20part%20of%20our%20problem%20is%20exactly%20--%20because%20in%202020%20agreements%20were%20disregarded%20and%20the%20mutuality%20on%20which%20this%20whole%20relationship%20is%20predicated%20has%20not%20been%20followed%20--%20we%20have%20the%20situation%2C%20we%20have.%20So%2C%20when%20you%20ask%20me%2C%20where%20will%20it%20go%20--%20I%20would%20say%2C%20lot%20of%20it%20will%20depend%20on%20what%20is%20the%20Chinese%20policy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20emphasized%20that%20the%20development%20of%20India-China%20relations%20is%20guided%20by%20three%20mutuals%20of%20respect%2C%20sensitivity%2C%20and%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20various%20mind%20games%20played%20by%20diplomats%20and%20politicians%20while%20dealing%20with%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20playing%20mind%20games%20with%20China%2C%20the%20EAM%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20we%20always%20lost%2C%20but%20I%20would%20argue%20that%20at%20various%20points%20of%20times%2C%20we%20could%20have%20--%20when%20we%20talk%20about%20the%20past%2C%20today%20would%20be%20very%20difficult%20for%20someone%20to%20understand.%20The%20Panchsheel%20Agreement%20is%20another%20such%20example.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704182760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-09%2Fd41je53g_india-china-border-arunachal-pradesh-reuters_625x300_02_September_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankars-swipe-at-nehrus-pm-modi-sardar-patel-china-approach-romanticism-vs-realism-4785101%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22EAM%20S%20Jaishankar%20has%20reiterated%20that%20India%20should%20deal%20with%20China%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20realism%20and%20asserted%20that%20the%20relationship%20should%20be%20based%20on%20the%20three%20mutual%20understandings-%20respect%2C%20sensitivity%2C%20and%20interest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankars-swipe-at-nehrus-pm-modi-sardar-patel-china-approach-romanticism-vs-realism-4785101%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankars-swipe-at-nehrus-pm-modi-sardar-patel-china-approach-romanticism-vs-realism-4785101%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankars-swipe-at-nehrus-pm-modi-sardar-patel-china-approach-romanticism-vs-realism-4785101%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Why%20Homegrown%20Akash%20Missile%20System%20Seen%20As%20India's%20'Iron%20Dome'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20homegrown%20surface-to-air%20missile%20(SAM)%20system%20Akash%20is%20getting%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20from%20other%20nations%20as%20they%20consider%20buying%20the%20advanced%20weapons%20platform.%20Developed%20by%20the%20Defence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20(DRDO)%20and%20produced%20by%20Bharat%20Dynamics%20Ltd%20(BDL)%2C%20Akash%20is%20a%20short-range%20SAM%20that%20can%20protect%20vulnerable%20areas%20and%20points%20from%20air%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DRDO%20has%20said%20India%20is%20the%20first%20nation%20that%20made%20a%20system%20capable%20of%20engaging%20four%20aerial%20targets%20at%20the%20same%20time%20at%2025%20km%20range%20by%20command%20guidance%20using%20a%20single%20firing%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20some%20key%20points%20about%20the%20Akash%20SAM%2C%20which%20is%20also%20being%20seen%20as%20India's%20%26quot%3BIron%20Dome%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20system%20used%20by%20Israel%20to%20intercept%20incoming%20rocket%20barrages.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20Armenia%2C%20Brazil%2C%20and%20Egypt%20have%20shown%20interest%20on%20the%20Akash%20SAM.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Akash%20weapon%20system%20can%20engage%20multiple%20targets%20at%20the%20same%20time%20in%20a%20group%20or%20autonomous%20mode.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAkash%20has%20built-in%20electronic%20counter-counter%20measures%20(ECCM)%20features%2C%20which%20can%20help%20the%20missile%20punch%20through%20enemy%20jamming%20and%20other%20methods%20of%20evasion.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20entire%20Akash%20weapon%20system%20has%20been%20configured%20on%20mobile%20platforms.%20This%20makes%20it%20agile%20and%20nimble%20as%20it%20can%20be%20transported%20fast%20anywhere.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Akash%20mobile%20system%20also%20enhances%20its%20survivability%20by%20moving%20from%20one%20place%20to%20another%20after%20firing%20missiles%20and%20before%20the%20enemy%20can%20launch%20a%20counter-attack%2C%20mostly%20with%20anti-radiation%20missiles%20that%20home%20in%20on%20radar%20emissions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Akash%20is%20in%20service%20with%20both%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF).%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAkash's%20comparison%20with%20Israel's%20Iron%20Dome%20comes%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Indian%20system%2C%20which%20is%20much%20larger%20than%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20missiles%2C%20can%20also%20intercept%20unmanned%20aerial%20vehicles%20(UAVs)%20and%20other%20types%20of%20smaller%20incoming%20projectiles%2C%20apart%20from%20helicopters%20and%20aircraft.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Akash%20system%2C%20however%2C%20is%20seen%20mainly%20for%20defence%20against%20bigger%20aerial%20threats%20like%20aircraft%2C%20than%20small%20rockets%20that%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20is%20mostly%20used%20to%20intercept.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Akash%20SAM%20can%20hit%20targets%20between%204.5%20km%20to%2025%20km%2C%20with%20an%20effective%20altitude%20of%20100%20meters%20to%2020%20km.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20missile%20is%205%2C870%20mm%20long%2C%20has%20a%20diameter%20of%20350%20mm%2C%20and%20weighs%20710%20kg.%20It%20can%20be%20made%20fully%20automatic%20with%20a%20quick%20response%20time%20from%20target%20detection%20to%20kill.%20Its%20open-system%20architecture%20ensures%20adaptability%20to%20existing%20and%20futuristic%20air%20defence%20environments.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704182700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fjristrdo_akash-missile_625x300_02_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-why-homegrown-akash-missile-system-is-seen-as-indias-iron-dome-4785731%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20homegrown%20surface-to-air%20missile%20(SAM)%20system%20Akash%20is%20getting%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20from%20other%20nations%20as%20they%20consider%20buying%20the%20advanced%20weapons%20platform.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-why-homegrown-akash-missile-system-is-seen-as-indias-iron-dome-4785731%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-why-homegrown-akash-missile-system-is-seen-as-indias-iron-dome-4785731%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-why-homegrown-akash-missile-system-is-seen-as-indias-iron-dome-4785731%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2248%20Dead%2C%20Several%20Feared%20Trapped%20As%20155%20Earthquakes%20Hit%20Japan%20In%20A%20Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2048%20people%20are%20confirmed%20dead%20following%20a%20major%20earthquake%20in%20Japan%2C%20a%20local%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20in%20Ishikawa%20prefecture%2C%20who%20spoke%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20told%20AFP%20the%20%26quot%3Bdeath%20count%20has%20reached%2048%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%207.5-magnitude%20quake%2C%20which%20hit%20Ishikawa%20prefecture%20on%20the%20main%20island%20of%20Honshu%2C%20triggered%20tsunami%20waves%20more%20than%20a%20metre%20high%2C%20toppled%20buildings%2C%20caused%20a%20major%20fire%20and%20tore%20apart%20roads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20daylight%20broke%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20destruction%20on%20the%20Noto%20Peninsula%20emerged%20with%20buildings%20still%20on%20fire%2C%20houses%20flattened%2C%20fishing%20boats%20sunk%20or%20washed%20ashore%20and%20highways%20hit%20by%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20such%20a%20powerful%20jolt%2C%26quot%3B%20Tsugumasa%20Mihara%2C%2073%2C%20told%20AFP%20as%20he%20queued%20with%20hundreds%20of%20others%20for%20water%20in%20the%20shellshocked%20town%20of%20Shika.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20a%20terrible%20way%20to%20start%20the%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20extensive%20damage%20has%20been%20confirmed%2C%20including%20numerous%20casualties%2C%20building%20collapses%20and%20fires%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Fumio%20Kishida%20said%20after%20a%20disaster%20response%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20race%20against%20time%20to%20search%20for%20and%20rescue%20victims%20of%20the%20disaster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAerial%20news%20footage%20showed%20the%20terrifying%20scale%20of%20a%20fire%20that%20ripped%20through%20Wajima%2C%20where%20a%20seven-storey%20commercial%20also%20building%20collapsed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%2033%2C000%20households%20were%20without%20power%20in%20the%20region%2C%20which%20saw%20temperatures%20touch%20freezing%20overnight%2C%20the%20local%20energy%20provider%20said.%20Many%20cities%20were%20without%20running%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Geological%20Survey%20(USGS)%20said%20the%20quake%20had%20a%20magnitude%20of%207.5.%20Japan's%20meteorological%20agency%20measured%20it%20at%207.6%20and%20said%20it%20was%20one%20of%20more%20than%20150%20to%20shake%20the%20region%20through%20Tuesday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20strong%20jolts%20were%20felt%20early%20Tuesday%2C%20including%20one%20measuring%205.6%20that%20prompted%20national%20broadcaster%20NHK%20to%20switch%20to%20a%20special%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20take%20deep%20breaths%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20presenter%20said%2C%20reminding%20viewers%20to%20check%20for%20fires%20in%20their%20kitchens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETsunami%20warning%20lifted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20waves%20at%20least%201.2%20metres%20(four%20feet)%20high%20hit%20Wajima%20and%20a%20series%20of%20smaller%20tsunamis%20were%20reported%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWarnings%20of%20much%20larger%20waves%20proved%20unfounded%20and%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Japan%20lifted%20all%20tsunami%20warnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImages%20on%20social%20media%20showed%20cars%2C%20houses%20and%20bridges%20in%20Ishikawa%20wobbling%20violently%20as%20terrified%20people%20cowered%20in%20shops%20and%20train%20stations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHouses%20collapsed%20and%20huge%20cracks%20appeared%20in%20roads%20while%20others%20were%20hit%20by%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20team%20of%20firefighters%20crawled%20under%20a%20collapsed%20commercial%20building%20Wajima%20looking%20for%20survivors%2C%20television%20footage%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHang%20in%20there!%20Hang%20in%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20shouted%20as%20they%20battled%20through%20piles%20of%20wooden%20beams%20with%20an%20electric%20saw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20in%20Wajima%20engulfed%20dozens%20of%20structures%2C%20video%20footage%20showed%2C%20with%20people%20being%20evacuated%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20some%20with%20blankets%20and%20others%20carrying%20babies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENHK%20reported%20that%2025%20houses%20had%20collapsed%20in%20the%20city%2C%20including%2014%20that%20may%20have%20had%20people%20trapped%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20duty%20officer%20at%20the%20Wajima%20Fire%20Department%20said%20authorities%20were%20still%20being%20overwhelmed%20Tuesday%20by%20rescue%20requests%20and%20reports%20of%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIshikawa%20Governor%20Hiroshi%20Hase%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20that%20roads%20have%20been%20cut%20in%20widespread%20areas%20by%20landslides%20or%20cracking%2C%20while%20in%20the%20port%20of%20Suzu%20%26quot%3Bmultiple%26quot%3B%20vessels%20had%20capsized.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%2062%2C000%20people%20had%20been%20ordered%20to%20evacuate%2C%20according%20to%20the%20fire%20and%20disaster%20management%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%201%2C000%20were%20staying%20at%20a%20military%20base%2C%20the%20defence%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBullet%20trains%20suspended%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefense%20Minister%20Minoru%20Kihara%20said%201%2C000%20military%20personnel%20were%20preparing%20to%20go%20to%20the%20region%2C%20while%208%2C500%20others%20were%20on%20standby.%20Around%2020%20military%20aircraft%20were%20dispatched%20to%20survey%20the%20damage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonday's%20quake%20shook%20apartments%20in%20the%20capital%20Tokyo%20about%20300%20kilometres%20away%2C%20where%20a%20public%20New%20Year%20greeting%20event%20that%20was%20to%20be%20attended%20by%20Emperor%20Naruhito%20and%20his%20family%20members%20was%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20major%20highways%20were%20closed%20around%20the%20epicentre%2C%20Japan's%20road%20operator%20said%2C%20and%20bullet%20train%20services%20from%20Tokyo%20were%20also%20suspended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20500%20people%20were%20stranded%20at%20Noto's%20damaged%20airport%2C%20with%20access%20roads%20blocked%20and%20the%20runway%20riddled%20with%20cracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20some%201%2C000%20people%20remained%20stuck%20in%20local%20express%20trains%20almost%2024%20hours%20after%20they%20were%20halted%20on%20Monday%2C%20NHK%20said.%3