0to%20book%20the%20SUV%20through%20the%20company's%20official%20website%20or%20dealerships%20by%20paying%20a%20nominal%20token%20amount%20of%20Rs%2025%2C000.%20The%20new%20Creta%20features%20a%20redesigned%20front%20fascia%2C%20including%20a%20wide%20three-row%20radiator%20grille%20and%20revised%20headlights.%20Inside%2C%20it%20offers%20hi-tech%20features%20and%20a%20comprehensive%20display.%20The%20SUV%20will%20be%20available%20with%20three%20engine%20options%20and%20four%20transmission%20choices.%20It%20will%20also%20come%20in%20several%20mono-tone%20and%20dual-tone%20color%20options.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22YASH%20SHARMA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fcars%2F2024-hyundai-cretas-unique-and-new-design-revealed-cabin-gets-stunning-look%2Farticleshow%2F106479662.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Arun%20Yogiraj%2C%20Sculptor%20Whose%20Idol%20May%20Be%20Chosen%20For%20Ayodhya%20Temple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EEven%20though%20an%20official%20announcement%20is%20awaited%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20has%20said%20that%20the%20idol%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20carved%20by%20Karnataka%20sculptor%20Arun%20Yogiraj%C2%A0will%20be%20installed%20at%20the%20grand%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Mr%20Yogiraj%20is%20one%20of%20the%20three%20sculptors%20whose%2051-inch%20idols%C2%A0were%20being%20considered%20to%20be%20placed%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMembers%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20trust%20refused%20to%20confirm%20that%20the%20Karnataka%20sculptor's%20entry%20has%20been%20chosen.%20A%20member%20of%20the%20trust%20told%20NDTV%20that%20%26quot%3Beverything%20is%20speculation%26quot%3B%20till%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra's%20secretary%20Champat%20Rai%20makes%20an%20official%20announcement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMBA%20graduate%20to%20sculptor%3A%20Who%20is%20Arun%20Yogiraj%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E1)%20Arun%20Yogiraj%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20sought-after%20sculptors%20in%20the%20country%2C%20comes%20from%20a%20family%20with%20a%20rich%20legacy%20of%20the%20craft.%20His%20father%20and%20grandfather%20were%20renowned%20sculptors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E2)%20After%20completing%20his%20MBA%2C%20Mr%20Yogiraj%20worked%20in%20a%20private%20company%20for%20a%20while%20but%20his%20heart%20was%20always%20set%20on%20continuing%20what%20four%20of%20his%20previous%20generations%20had%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E3)%20Mr%20Yogiraj's%20work%20has%20earned%20him%20recognition%20from%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E4)%20The%2030-foot%20statue%20of%20Subhash%20Chandra%20Bose%2C%20a%20centre%20of%20attraction%20in%20the%20grand%20canopy%20behind%20the%20Amar%20Jawan%20Jyoti%20at%20the%20India%20Gate%2C%20was%20also%20crafted%20by%20Mr%20Yogiraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E5)%20Among%20his%20other%20works%2C%20a%2012-foot-tall%20statue%20of%20Adi%20Shankaracharya%20in%20Kedarnath%20and%20a%2021-foot-tall%20Hanuman%20statue%20at%20Chunchanakatte%20in%20Mysore%20district%20have%20been%20widely%20covered%20in%20the%20media.%20Arun%20has%20also%20sculpted%20a%2015-foot-tall%20statue%20of%20Dr%20BR%20Ambedkar.%20The%20royal%20family%20of%20Mysore%20has%20also%20paid%20special%20respects%20to%20his%20contribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BDream%20come%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EArun%20Yogiraj's%20wife%20Vijetha%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20family%20was%20thrilled%20and%20felt%20their%20desires%20had%20been%20fulfilled.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20a%20dream%20come%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESpeaking%20of%20her%20husband's%20dedication%20to%20his%20craft%2C%20she%20said%20that%20Arun%20Yogiraj%20works%20for%2010%20hours%20every%20day%2C%20adding%20for%20projects%20with%20national%20importance%2C%20he%20would%20work%20round%20the%20clock.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20room%20for%20error%20when%20he%20is%20carving.%20He%20creates%20a%20masterpiece%20every%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EArun%20Yogiraj%20spoke%20with%20his%20wife%20about%20the%20task%20at%20hand.%20%26quot%3BHe%20had%20said%20it%20was%20difficult%2C%20but%20he%20would%20keep%20carving%20till%20he%20found%20Lord%20Ram%20in%20the%20idol.%20He%20had%20said%20Lord%20Ram%20would%20help%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Vijetha%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Arun%20Yogiraj's%20mother%20Saraswathi%20is%20extremely%20happy%20that%20the%20entire%20world%20will%20soon%20see%20the%20work%20of%20her%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3ERam%20Lalla%20Idol%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20January%201%2C%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20that%20the%20selection%20of%20the%20idol%20for%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtapana%20of%20Lord%20Rama%20in%20Ayodhya%20had%20been%20finalised.%20%26quot%3BRenowned%20sculptor%20of%20our%20country%2C%20our%20proud%20Mr%20Arun%20Yogiraj.%20The%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Rama%20carved%20by%20him%20will%20be%20installed%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said%20in%20the%20post%20in%20Kannada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20another%20example%20of%20Rama%20Hanuman's%20inextricable%20relationship.%20There%20is%20no%20mistaking%20that%20this%20is%20an%20important%20service%20to%20Ramlallani%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20land%20of%20Hanuman.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BThe%20selection%20of%20the%20idol%20for%20the%20Prana%20Pratishtapana%20of%20Lord%20Rama%20in%20Ayodhya%20has%20been%20finalized.%20The%20idol%20of%20Lord%20Rama%2C%20carved%20by%20renowned%20sculptor%20of%20our%20country%20Yogiraj%20Arun%2C%20will%20be%20installed%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%26quot%3B%20tweets%20Union%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn(Image%20source%3A%20Union%20Minister%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FeChIG9rXGT%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FeChIG9rXGT%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1741989714037817769%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%202%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Teertha%20Kshetra%20trust%2C%20the%20body%20overseeing%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20make%20an%20official%20announcement%20on%20the%20selection%20of%20the%20idol%20on%20January%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20selection%2C%20three%20idols%20were%20in%20consideration.%20Asked%20about%20the%20parameters%20of%20the%20selection%20process%2C%20trust%20member%20Bimlendra%20Mohan%20Pratap%20Mishra%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bidol%20speaks%20to%20you%20and%20you%20get%20mesmerised%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Champat%20Rai%20told%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20one%20with%20the%20most%20divine%20look%20and%20bearing%20a%20distinct%20impression%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20would%20be%20selected%20for%20Pran%20Pratishtha.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704182100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F5rasv9f_arun-yogiraj_625x300_02_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-arun-yogiraj-sculptor-whose-ram-lalla-idol-may-be-chosen-for-ayodhya-temple-4785329%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmbhoomi%20Teertha%20Kshetra%20trust%2C%20the%20body%20overseeing%20the%2