%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%2C%20has%20addressed%20allegations%20and%20criticisms%20against%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20functioning%20and%20judgements%20%E2%80%93%20largely%20by%20doubling%20down%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArticle%20370%20judgment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five-judge%20bench%E2%80%99s%20verdict%20upholding%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20of%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20been%20lambasted%20by%20several%20experts%20and%20legal%20commentators%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjustice-nariman-speech-election-commission-article-370-supreme-court-bbc-media%5C%22%3Eincluding%20former%20Supreme%20Court%20judges.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20PTI%2C%20the%20CJI%20who%20headed%20the%20bench%20said%20that%20it%20would%20not%20appropriate%20to%20%E2%80%9Ceither%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20criticism%20or%20mount%20a%20defence%20to%20%5Bhis%5D%20judgement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20have%20said%20in%20my%20judgement%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20reason%20present%20in%20the%20signed%20judgement%20and%20I%20must%20leave%20it%20at%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20a%20judgment%20is%20public%20property%20once%20delivered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJudges%20who%20decide%20a%20case%20speak%20through%20their%20Judgement.%20Once%20a%20Judgement%20is%20delivered%20that%20judgement%20becomes%20a%20public%20property%20of%20the%20nation.%20Until%20a%20judgement%20is%20delivered%20the%20process%20is%20confined%20to%20the%20judges%20who%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20decision%20of%20that%20case.%20Once%20we%20arrive%20at%20a%20decision%20and%20the%20judgement%20is%20pronounced%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20public%20property.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20property%20of%20the%20nation.%20We%20are%20a%20free%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpeople%20are%20entitled%20to%20exercise%20their%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression.%20To%20critique%2C%20to%20criticise%2C%20to%20appreciate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESame-sex%20marriage%20verdict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20much-criticised%20judgment%20in%20the%20pleas%20for%20legal%20sanction%20to%20same-sex%20marriage%20by%20a%20bench%20headed%20by%20the%20CJI%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20has%20no%20regrets%20and%20that%20judges%20do%20not%20associate%20themselves%20with%20a%20cause.%20The%20bench%20refused%20to%20legally%20recognise%20same-sex%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20leave%20it%20for%20the%20future%20of%20our%20society%20to%20judge%20which%20course%20to%20take%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20minority%20view%2C%20the%20CJI%20and%20now-retired%20Justice%20S.K.%20Kaul%20said%20that%20they%20do%20recognise%20the%20right%20of%20same-sex%20couples%20to%20enter%20into%20marriages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20told%20PTI%20that%20training%20teaches%20judges%20to%20distance%20themselves%20from%20the%20outcome%20once%20they%20deliver%20a%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COutcomes%20are%20never%2C%20in%20that%20sense%2C%20something%20which%20are%20personal%20to%20a%20judge.%20You%20decide%20a%20case%20based%20on%20your%20vision%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20on%20what%20you%20believe%20the%20vision%20of%20a%20just%20society%20for%20the%20future%20is%2C%20in%20constitutional%20terms%2C%20which%20is%20what%20I%20have%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAllocation%20and%20lawyers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20appeared%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20allegation%20by%20senior%20lawyers%20like%20Prashant%20Bhushan%20and%20Dushyant%20Dave%20on%20important%20matters%20often%20being%20reassigned%20to%20separate%20judges%20than%20who%20had%20already%20heard%20a%20part%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20very%2C%20very%20clear%20in%20my%20mind%20that%20if%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20institution%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20to%20be%20maintained%2C%20we%20have%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20allocation%20of%20cases%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20a%20lawyer-driven%20allocation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20allocation%20has%20to%20be%20according%20to%20%E2%80%9Cterms%20of%20our%20system%20laid%20down%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20to%20trust%20your%20decision%20makers%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20said%2C%20upholding%20the%20roster%20%E2%80%93%20which%20he%20heads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20no%20lawyer%20can%20insist%20that%20their%20case%20will%20be%20heard%20by%20a%20particular%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20does%20not%20do%20justice%20either%20to%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20individual%20judge%20or%20the%20purity%20of%20the%20administration%20of%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAyodhya%20verdict%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20said%20that%20the%20five-judges%20who%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20Ram%20temple%E2%80%99s%20construction%20on%20the%20site%20that%20had%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20on%20it%2C%20had%20unanimously%20decided%20there%20will%20be%20no%20authorship%20ascribed%20to%20the%20judgement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSupreme%20Court%20judgement%20on%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20was%20the%20judgement%20of%20the%20court%2C%20not%20any%20individual.%20So%20the%20author%20of%20the%20judgement%20was%20not%20named.%20It%20was%20a%20case%20of%20long%20conflict%20and%20diverse%20viewpoints%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20explanation%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSauravDassss%2Fstatus%2F1742033395645890943%5C%22%3Emet%20with%20some%20criticism%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20commentators%20who%20have%20said%20that%20all%20judgments%20are%20those%20of