india-news%2Fvideo-long-queues-at-maharashtra-petrol-pumps-amid-hit-and-run-protests-4785161%5C%22%3Elong%20queues%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20days.%20No%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20rush%20to%20fill%20up%20tanks%20before%20prices%20go%20up.%20This%20is%20panic%20buying%20amid%20apprehensions%20that%20the%20truckers'%20protest%20against%20the%20soon-to-be-implemented%20criminal%20code%20will%20hit%20supply.%20If%20the%20protest%20drags%20on%2C%20it%20may%20hit%20supply%20of%20other%20essential%20supplies%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Are%20Truckers%20Protesting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtests%20have%20broken%20out%20in%20several%20states%2C%20including%20Bihar%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20against%20the%20high%20penalties%20for%20hit-and-run%20accidents%20in%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%20which%20is%20set%20to%20replace%20the%20colonial-era%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20law%2C%20hit-and-run%20cases%20can%20attract%20up%20to%2010%20years%20in%20jail%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%207%20lakh.%20Truckers%2C%20cab%20drivers%20and%20others%20operating%20commercial%20vehicles%20are%20asking%20how%20they%20would%20pay%20such%20a%20high%20fine%20in%20the%20event%20of%20an%20accident.%20Happy%20Sidhu%2C%20president%20of%20All%20Punjab%20Truck%20Operators'%20Union%2C%20called%20the%20new%20law%20a%20%26quot%3Bblack%20law%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20destroy%20truckers%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtest%20Hitting%20Supply%20Lines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrivers%20of%20thousands%20of%20tankers%20that%20transport%20fuel%20to%20pumps%20are%20part%20of%20the%20protest.%20With%20them%20joining%20the%20strike%2C%20fuel%20crisis%20has%20already%20gripped%20several%20cities%20and%20other%20urban%20centres%20fear%20a%20similar%20situation%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20An%20association%20of%20petrol%20pump%20dealers%20in%20Aurangabad%20have%20said%20fuel%20pumps%20in%20the%20district%20may%20go%20dry%20by%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDrivers%20of%20tankers%20that%20carry%20fuel%20from%20Panewadi%20(in%20Nashik)%20have%20called%20for%20agitation%20and%20have%20stopped%20filling%20fuel%2C%26quot%3B%20Aqeel%20Abbas%2C%20secretary%20of%20the%20association%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%20At%20Himachal%20in%20the%20north%2C%20the%20strike%20has%20already%20hit%20the%20tourism%20sector.%20Local%20media%20reports%20have%20said%20tourists%20are%20struggling%20to%20find%20vehicles%20after%20cab%20operators%20joined%20the%20strike%20against%20the%20new%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnil%20Garg%2C%20president%20of%20Maharashtra%20school%20bus%20owners'%20association%2C%20said%20school%20buses%20would%20operate%20till%20they%20run%20out%20of%20diesel.%20%26quot%3BIf%20diesel%20supply%20stops%2C%20school%20buses%20will%20stop%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtests%20From%20Patna%20To%20Pune%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETyres%20were%20burnt%20and%20roads%20blocked%20in%20Patna%20as%20truck%20operators%20raised%20slogans%20against%20the%20new%20law%2C%20questioning%20who%20will%20feed%20their%20families%20if%20they%20stay%20in%20jail%20for%2010%20years.%20In%20Navi%20Mumbai%2C%20a%20group%20of%20truckers%20attacked%20a%20policeman%20early%20this%20morning.%20The%20cops%20had%20to%20use%20force%20to%20disperse%20the%20mob%20on%20Mumbai-Bengaluru%20highway%2C%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Thane%2C%20the%20protesters%20blocked%20Mumbai-Ahmedabad%20Highway%20and%20threw%20stones%20at%20police.%20A%20policeman%20was%20injured%20and%20a%20police%20vehicle%20damaged.%20At%20Dhar%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20private%20bus%20and%20truck%20drivers%20blocked%20the%20Pitampur%20highway.%20Protests%20were%20held%20in%20Bhopal%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20capital%20Raipur%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Are%20Protesters%20Saying%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20why%20they%20are%20protesting%2C%20Bhopal%20cab%20driver%20Gyansingh%20Yadav%20broke%20down.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20like%20me%20who%20drive%20cabs%20for%20a%20living%20still%20go%20home%20at%20night.%20But%20truck%20drivers%20often%20don't%20meet%20their%20loved%20ones%20for%2015%20days%20or%20more.%20We%20are%20not%20against%20any%20government%20or%20law%2C%20but%20I%20feel%20some%20amendments%20should%20be%20made%2C%20especially%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20penal%20provisions%20against%20drivers.%20The%20new%20law%20attracts%20a%2010-year%20prison%20term%20for%20errant%20drivers.%20I%20feel%20it%20should%20be%20reduced%20to%201-2%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Raipur%2C%20a%20bus%20driver%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20poor%20people.%20Penal%20action%20should%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20owners%20of%20our%20vehicles.%20This%20law%20is%20unfair%20on%20us.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20on%20strike%20till%20our%20demands%20are%20met.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Aurangabad%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20truck%20driver%20Syed%20Wajed%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20drivers%2C%20how%20can%20we%20pay%20such%20a%20huge%20fine%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20The%20Law%2C%20What's%20The%20Change%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHit-and-run%20accidents%20and%20death%20due%20to%20rash%20driving%20is%20covered%20under%20the%20law%20for%20causing%20death%20by%20negligence.%20In%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita.%20The%20law%2C%20which%20has%20received%20the%20President's%20assent%20after%20it%20cleared%20Parliament%2C%20has%20two%20clauses%20under%20Section%20104.%20%26quot%3BWhoever%20causes%20the%20death%20of%20any%20person%20by%20doing%20any%20rash%20or%20negligent%20act%C2%A0not%20amounting%20to%20culpable%20homicide%2C%20shall%20be%20punished%20with%20imprisonment%20of%20either%20description%20for%20a%20term%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20the%20first%20clause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhoever%20causes%20death%20of%20any%20person%20by%20doing%20any%20rash%20or%20negligent%20act%20not%20amounting%20to%20culpable%20homicide%20and%20escapes%20from%20the%20scene%20of%20incident%20or%20fails%20to%20report%20the%20incident%20to%20a%20Police%20officer%20or%20Magistrate%20soon%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20shall%20be%20punished%20with%20imprisonment%20of%20either%20description%20of%20a%20term%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20ten%20years%2C%20and%20shall%20also%20be%20liable%20to%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20the%20second.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20hit-and-run%20accidents%20are%20covered%20by%20IPC's%20Section%20304A.%20%26quot%3BWhoever%20causes%20the%20death%20of%20any%20person%20by%20doing%20any%20rash%C2%A0or%20negligent%20act%20not%20amounting%20to%20culpable%20homicide%2C%20shall%20be%20punished%20with%20imprisonment%20of%20either%20description%20for%20a%20term%20which%20may%20extend%20to%20two%20years%2C%20or%20with%20fine%2C%20or%20with%20both%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704180060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fg423mleg_fuel-rush_625x300_02_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpetrol-pumps-hit-and-run-bharatiya-nyaya-sanhita-from-patna-to-thane-truckers-hit-streets-to-protest-new-hit-and-run-law-4785344%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fuel%20pumps%20in%20several%20states%20are%20witnessing%20long%20queues%20over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20days.%20No%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20rush%20to%20fill%20up%20tanks%20before%20prices%20go%20up.%20This%20is%20panic%20buying%20amid%20apprehensions%20that%20the%20truckers'%20protest%20against%20the%20new%20law%20will%20hit%20supply%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpetrol-pumps-hit