_Deependra_Singh_Hooda_GOC-in-C_Northern_Command_Indian_Army.jpg%20450w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F02114145%2FLieutenant_General_Deependra_Singh_Hooda_GOC-in-C_Northern_Command_Indian_Army-288x300.jpg%20288w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691265%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERetired%20Lieutenant%20General%20Deependra%20Singh%20Hooda.%20Photo%3A%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGujjar-Bakharwals%20are%20nomads%20and%20have%20traditionally%20supported%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20have%20been%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20reasons%20behind%20the%20roll%20back%20of%20insurgency%20from%20Jammu%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hooda%20said.%20Rukhsana%20Kausar%20KC%2C%20a%20young%20Gujjar%20woman%20from%20Upper%20Kalsi%2C%20had%20shot%20down%20a%20Lashkar-e-Toiba%20militant%20in%20Rajouri%20district%20in%202009%2C%20the%20paper%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2024%2Fjan%2F02%2Farmy-should-win-back-gujjars-to-contain-militancy-2647040.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20seems%20to%20be%20some%20laxity%20in%20procedures%2C%20which%20may%20have%20developed%20during%20the%20long%20militancy-free%20period%20(Poonch%2C%20Rajouri%20were%20declared%20militancy%20free%20by%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20police%20in%202011).%20How%20much%20did%20we%20lose%20out%20on%20the%20local%20connect%20when%20nothing%20was%20happening%3F%E2%80%9D%20the%20Army%20veteran%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20year%2C%20these%20nomadic%20communities%20move%20along%20with%20their%20herds%20of%20sheep%20between%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%20and%20Poonch%2C%20Rajouri%20in%20Pir%20Panjal%20belt%20and%20carry%20very%20useful%20information.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20an%20urgent%20need%20to%20build%20back%20the%20old%20connection%20with%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hooda%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%