d%20up%20by%20the%20Army%20died%20in%20custody%2C%20leading%20to%20anger%20within%20the%20community.%20A%20video%20clip%20showing%20uniformed%20soldiers%20from%2048%20Rashtriya%20Rifles%20torturing%20the%20men%20also%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media.%20Mobile%20internet%20was%20shut%20down%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20attempt%20to%20mitigate%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20unrest%2C%20on%20December%2024%2C%20the%20Army%20removed%20the%20brigade%20commander%20and%20three%20other%20officers%20of%2013%20Rashtriya%20Rifles.%20The%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20police%20also%20registered%20an%20FIR%20against%20unknown%20persons%20under%20Section%20302%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20for%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2027%2C%20Union%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%2C%20accompanied%20by%20Lt.%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20and%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20General%20Manoj%20Pande%2C%20visited%20the%20Poonch%20sector%20to%20review%20the%20situation.%20During%20their%20visit%2C%20they%20also%20met%20with%20the%20families%20of%20the%20three%20deceased%20civilians%20and%20assuring%20them%20of%20speedy%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704176821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F23153648%2FEffect-44.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fgujjar-bakharwal-jammu-kashmir-army-general-hooda%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Gujjar-Bakharwals%20are%20nomads%20and%20have%20traditionally%20supported%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20have%20been%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20reasons%20behind%20the%20roll%20back%20of%20insurgency%20from%20Jammu.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fgujjar-bakharwal-jammu-kashmir-army-general-hooda%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Thailand%20and%20China%20to%20waive%20visa%20requirement