i%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20he%20fell%20for%20the%20scam%20because%20he%20thought%20it%20was%20related%20to%20a%20recently%20lost%20card.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20advice%20for%20people%20who%20think%20they%20might%20be%20getting%20scammed%20is%3A%20%26quot%3Bjust%20go%20to%20your%20bank%20branch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fandy-cohen-biography-life-pictures-family-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndy%20Cohen%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20he%20lost%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20money%26quot%3B%20to%20scammers%20who%20pretended%20to%20be%20from%20his%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20recent%20episode%20of%20his%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Fshow%2F57jS8KqYiN59LVd15QMux7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDaddy%20Diaries%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20co-hosted%20by%20John%20Hill%2C%20Cohen%20recounted%20how%20he%20unwittingly%20became%20a%20victim%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscam-bank-fraud-texts-on-the-rise-ftc-warns-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebank%20fraud%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3BWatch%20What%20Happens%20Live!%26quot%3B%20host%20explained%20that%20he%20fell%20for%20the%20scam%20because%20he%20thought%20it%20was%20related%20to%20a%20card%20he%20had%20recently%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20gotten%20an%20email%20on%20Sunday%20because%20I%20did%20lose%20a%20card%2C%20and%20I%20put%20in%20for%20it%2C%20and%20I%20got%20an%20email%20being%20like%2C%20'There%20might%20be%20fraud%20on%20your%20account.%20And%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20this%20is%20attached%20to%20the%20card%20I%20lost%2C'%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20said%20on%20the%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20impression%20that%20he%20was%20interacting%20with%20his%20bank%2C%20Cohen%20logged%20into%20his%20bank%20account%20but%20realized%20something%20was%20amiss%20when%20they%20asked%20for%20his%20Apple%20ID%20and%20password.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20was%20like%2C%20okay%2C%20this%20never%20happens%2C%20so%20I%20bailed%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2055-year-old%20said.%20Unfortunately%2C%20it%20was%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20had%20already%20logged%20into%20my%20bank%20app%2C%20and%20I%20think%20somehow%2C%20my%20logging%20in%20through%20whatever%20this%20site%20was%20gave%20them%20access%20to%20my%20bank%20app%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TV%20and%20radio%20host%20says%20he%20subsequently%20received%20a%20call%20that%20showed%20up%20with%20a%20caller%20ID%20that%20matched%20the%20name%20of%20his%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20he%20answered%20it%20under%20the%20belief%20it%20was%20legitimately%20from%20the%20bank's%20fraud%20alert%20team%20%E2%80%94%20who%20were%20calling%20about%20the%20earlier%20hacking%20%E2%80%94%20not%20realizing%20it%20was%20from%20the%20same%20scammers%20with%20a%20disguised%20caller%20ID.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20naming%20credits%20that%20I%20had%20made%20%E2%80%94%20charges%20%E2%80%94%20because%20they%20clearly%20had%20access%20to%20my%20account%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bstayed%20on%20the%20line%20with%20this%20woman%20for%20an%20hour%20and%2010%20minutes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20explained%20he%20was%20tricked%20into%20setting%20up%20call%20forwarding%20and%20message%20forwarding%20to%20the%20scammers%2C%20which%20meant%20that%20the%20bank%20couldn't%20reach%20him%20about%20the%20money%20transfers%20from%20his%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20calls%20were%20forwarded%20to%20the%20scammers%2C%20who%20then%20%26quot%3Bconfirmed%20the%20wires%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20people%20wired%2C%20out%20of%20two%20accounts%20that%20I%20have%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20added%20that%20he%20was%20still%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20process%26quot%3B%20of%20trying%20to%20get%20his%20money%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20shared%20that%20he%20called%20his%20parents%20after%20the%20incident%20to%20let%20them%20know%20what%20happened%20and%20how%20to%20protect%20themselves%20from%20falling%20into%20the%20same%20trap%20as%20he%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20think%20part%20of%20my%20advice%20for%20people%20is%3A%20If%20you%20feel%20something%20is%20happening%2C%20just%20go%20to%20your%20bank%20branch%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20when%20you%20get%20emails%2C%20look%20very%20closely%20at%20the%20email%20address%20they're%20coming%20from.%20It%20might%20say%20your%20bank's%20name%2C%20but%20click%20on%20the%20name%2C%20and%20then%20the%20email%20address%20will%20come%20up%2C%20and%20you'll%20see%20that%20it's%20some%20other%20random%20address.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20FBI's%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fbi.gov%2Fcontact-us%2Ffield-offices%2Fspringfield%2Fnews%2Finternet-crime-complaint-center-releases-2022-statistics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20phishing%20schemes%20were%20the%20most%20highly-reported%20internet%20crime%20in%202022.%20There%20were%20300%2C497%20complaints%20filed%2C%20with%20a%20loss%20amounting%20to%20%2452%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-phishing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPhishing%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20type%20of%20cybercrime%20where%20criminals%20get%20victims%20to%20give%20up%20personal%20or%20sensitive%20information%20by%20pretending%20to%20be%20someone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFraudsters%20can%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fphishing-scams-in-your-inbox-waiting-to-steal-your-money-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efake%20bank%20emails%20and%20fake%20shipping%20notifications%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20among%20other%20ploys%2C%20to%20scam%20victims%20of%20their%20money%20or%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fidentity-theft-by-state%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esteal%20their%20identities%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20scammers%20are%20also%20turning%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-voice-generator-phone-scam-imposter-crime-money-cash-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20to%20mimic%20the%20voices%20of%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20try%20to%20swindle%20their%20loved%20ones%20out%20of%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandy-cohen-victim-of-bank-fraud-scammers-phone-email-phishing-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704174964000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6593741dec62ab5daf7fdbf3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandy-cohen-victim-of-bank-fraud-scammers-phone-email-phishing-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20a%20recent%20episode%20of%20his%20%26quot%3BDaddy%20Diaries%26quot%3B%20podcast%2C%20co-hosted%20by%20John%20Hill%2C%20Andy%20Cohen%20recounted%20how%20he%20unwittingly%20became%20a%20victim%20of%20bank%20fraud.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandy-cohen-victim-of-bank-fraud-scammers-phone-email-phishing-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Given%20the%20Role%20of%20US%20in%20Blatantly%20Supporting%20Israel...'%2C%20Sandeep%20Pandey%20Returns%20Magsaysay%20Award%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F02105905%2FFu4KfacaUAAe7et.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%202002%2C%20social%20activist%20and%20current%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Socialist%20Party%20(India)%2C%20Sandeep%20Pandey%20was%20recognised%20by%20the%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%20Foundation%20as%20%E2%80%98an%20Indian%20who%20followed%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20path%20and%20supported%20education%20for%20poor%20children%20by%20tapping%20the%20resources%20of%20the%20Indian%20diaspora.%E2%80%99%20His%20organisation%2C%20Asha%20for%20Education%2C%20has%2012%20chapters%20and%20takes%20on%20the%20mantle%20of%20educating%20under-privileged%20kids%20with%20a%20view%20to%20shaping%20the%20socio-economic-political%20future%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98In%20electing%20Sandeep%20Pandey%20to%20receive%20the%202002%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%20for%20Emergent%20Leadership%2C%20the%20board%20of%20trustees%20recognizes%20the%20empowering%20example%20of%20his%20commitment%20to%20the%20transformation%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20marginalized%20poor%2C%E2%80%99%20the%20citation%20read.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOn%20January%201%2C%20Sandeep%20Pandey%20announced%20his%20decision%20to%20return%20the%20award%20and%20the%20degrees%20he%20got%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20role%20of%20the%20US%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20attack%20on%20Gaza.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBelow%20is%20his%20statement%20in%20full.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20received%20the%20Magsaysay%20Award%20in%202002%2C%20a%20little%20controversy%20was%20created%20due%20to%20my%20decision%20to%20participate%20in%20a%20protest%20outside%20United%20States%20embassy%20in%20Manila%20against%20the%20impending%20attack%20on%20Iraq%2C%20immediately%20a%20day%20after%20the%20award%20ceremony%20in%20which%20the%20award%20was%20handed%20over%20by%20the%20Phillippines%20President.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20then%20Chaiperson%20of%20Magsaysay%20Foundation%20had%20tried%20to%20dissuade%20me%20from%20participating%20in%20the%20protest%20on%20the%20pretext%20that%20it%E2%80%99ll%20harm%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20foundation.%20My%20contention%20was%20that%20the%20award%20mentioned%20my%20participation%20in%20a%20peace%20march%20in%20India%20for%20global%20nuclear%20disarmament%20from%20Pokaran%20to%20Sarnath%20in%201999%20and%20hence%20my%20anti-war%20position%20was%20well%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20honour%20the%20decision%20taken%20at%20a%20peace%20conference%20at%20University%20in%20Manila%20which%2C%20coincidently%2C%20concluded%20on%20August%2031%2C%20the%20day%20Magsaysay%20Awards%20were%20handed%20over%2C%20to%20stage%20a%20protest%20at%20US%20embassy%2C%20as%20I%20was%20invited%20to%20the%20conference%20as%20well.%20After%20the%20protest%20on%201%20September%2C%20a%20Manila%20newspaper%2C%20in%20an%20editorial%2C%20challenged%20me%20saying%20that%20if%20I%20was%20the%20principled%20man%20that%20I%20would%20like%20them%20to%20believe%20then%20I%20should%20return%20the%20award%20to%20the%20US%20embassy%20before%20returning%20to%20India%2C%20This%20made%20the%20decision%20easier%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20returned%20the%20cash%20component%20of%20the%20award%20from%20the%20airport%20which%20came%20from%20the%20Ford%20Foundation%20of%20the%20US%20but%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Chairperson%20of%20Magsaysay%20Foundation%20I%20said%20that%20for%20the%20time%20being%20I%20was%20keeping%20the%20award%20as%20it%20was%20named%20after%20a%20former%20popular%20Phillppines%20President%20and%20had%20been%20given%20in%20my%20country%20to%20personalities%20like%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%2C%20Vinoba%20Bhave%20and%20Baba%20Amte%2C%20whom%20I%20considered%20as%20my%20ideals.%20I%20had%20mentioned%20in%20that%20letter%20that%20if%20the%20Magsaysay%20Foundation%20ever%20thought%20that%20I%20was%20harming%20their%20reputation%20too%20much%2C%20I%20would%20be%20happy%20to%20return%20the%20award%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20think%20that%20the%20time%20has%20now%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMagsaysay%20Award%20is%20primarily%20funded%20by%20Rockefeller%20Foundation%20and%20the%20category%20in%20which%20I%20received%20the%20award%20is%20funded%20by%20Ford%20Foundation%2C%20both%20American%20foundations.%20Given%20the%20role%20of%20US%20in%20blatantly%20supporting%20Israel%20in%20the%20current%20offensive%20against%20Palestinian%20citizens%2C%20more%20than%2021%2C500%20of%20whom%20are%20dead%2C%20and%20still%20continuing%20to%20sell%20arms%20to%20Israel%2C%20it%20has%20become%20unbearable%20for%20me%20to%20keep%20the%20award.%20I%2C%20therefore%2C%20am%20deciding%20to%20finally%20return%20the%20award%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Funited-states-israel-palestine%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20Is%20Part%20of%20the%20Problem%20in%20Israel-Palestine%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20would%20like%20to%20apologise%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Phillippines%20if%20they%20feel%20hurt%20because%20of%20President%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%E2%80%99s%20name%20associated%20with%20this%20award.%20My%20protest%20is%20only%20because%20of%20the%20American%20connection%20with%20the%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20return%20the%20Magsaysay%20award%20I%20also%20feel%20that%20I%20should%20relieve%20myself%20of%20the%20degrees%20I%20have%20obtained%20in%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20I%20am%20also%20taking%20a%20decision%20to%20return%20my%20Dual%20M.S.%20degrees%20in%20Manufacturing%20and%20Computer%20Engineerings%20to%20Syracuse%20University%20in%20upstate%20New%20York%20and%20my%20Ph.D.%20in%20Mechanical%20Engineering%20degree%20to%20the%20University%20of%20California%20at%20Berkeley.%20Incidentally%2C%20I%20was%20made%20conscious%20of%20involvement%20of%20US%20academic%20institutions%2C%20especially%20their%20engineering%20and%20science%20departments%2C%20in%20defence%20projects%20during%20the%20protest%20on%20Berkeley%20campus%20in%201991%20against%20the%20US%20war%20on%20Iraq%20launched%20by%20senior%20President%20Bush.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Professor%20Pravin%20Varaiya%20of%20Electrical%20Engineering%2C%20whose%20research%20area%2C%20Control%20Systems%2C%20was%20same%20as%20mine%2C%20and%20who%20was%20a%20participant%20in%20the%20anti-was%20protests%2C%20made%20me%20realize%20that%20I%20was%20also%20unknowingly%20part%20of%20the%20war%20machine%20of%20United%20States.%20Thus%20began%20my%20disillusionment%20with%20my%20research%20area%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20change%20my%20research%20area%20once%20I%20began%20teaching%20at%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20at%20Kanpur%20in%201992.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgain%20let%20me%20make%20it%20clear%20that%20I%20am%20not%20against%20the%20American%20people%20or%20even%20the%20country.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20think%20the%20US%20is%20one%20country%20which%20respects%20the%20human%20rights%20the%20most%20and%20offers%20the%20best%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20but%20sadly%20it%20is%20true%20only%20within%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20US%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20have%20little%20regard%20for%20human%20rights%2C%20especially%20of%20the%20third%20world%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhy-israels-supporters-in-the-west-are-no-friends-of-jews%5C%22%3EWhy%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Supporters%20in%20the%20West%20Are%20No%20Friends%20of%20Jewish%20People%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20respects%20justice%20then%20it%20should%20stand%20with%20the%20side%20facing%20oppression%20in%20any%20war.%20It%20took%20the%20correct%20position%20in%20the%20Russian%20war%20on%20Ukraine%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Israel%20against%20Palestine%20it%20is%20inexplicable%20why%20the%20US%20chooses%20to%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20misfortunes%20and%20sufferings%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20overlooks%20the%20crimes%20of%20Israeli%20defence%20forces.%20Had%20it%20been%20any%20other%20country%2C%20it%20would%20have%20imposed%20sanctions%20against%20it%2C%20like%20it%20did%20along%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20against%20South%20Africa%2C%20when%20apartheid%20was%20still%20practiced%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20to%20take%20the%20hard%20decision%20because%20I%20think%20US%20is%20singularly%20responsible%20in%20encouraging%20Israel%20to%20continue%20its%20aggression%20against%20Palestinians%20contrary%20to%20the%20popular%20world%20opinion.%20It%20could%20have%20played%20the%20role%20of%20mediator%2C%20like%20it%20once%20did%2C%20and%20tried%20to%20negotiate%20peace%20between%20Israel%20and%20Palestine.%20Creation%20of%20sovereign%20state%20of%20Palestine%20and%20its%20recognition%20by%20United%20Nations%20as%20a%20full%20member%20is%20essential%20towards%20the%20solution%20of%20the%20problem.%20But%20it%20is%20strange%20that%20US%2C%20which%20not%20very%20long%20back%20handed%20over%20Afghanistan%2C%20much%20bigger%20in%20area%2C%20to%20Taliban%20on%20a%20silver%20platter%20knowing%20very%20well%20that%20it%20was%20jeopardising%20the%20civil%20liberties%20of%20common%20Afghans%2C%20especially%20the%20women%2C%20parrots%20the%20Israeli%20position%20about%20Hamas%20being%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20ignoring%20the%20fact%20that%20Hamas%20has%20won%20an%20election%20in%20Palestine%2C%20unlike%20the%20Taliban.%20I%20feel%20that%20it%20is%20time%20to%20call%20out%20the%20double%20standards%20of%20US%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESandeep%20Pandey%20is%20General%20Secretary%20of%20Socialist%20Party%20(India).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704174604000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F02105905%2FFu4KfacaUAAe7et.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fsandeep-pandey-magsaysay-award-return-israel-degrees%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'As%20I%20return%20the%20Magsaysay%20award%20I%20also%20feel%20that%20I%20should%20relieve%20myself%20of%20the%20degrees%20I%20have%20obtained%20in%20the%20US%2C'%20the%20activist%20wrote.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C