0threshold%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmajor%20tsunami%20warning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20reported%20that%20smaller%20tsunami%20waves%20had%20already%20been%20confirmed%20to%20have%20reached%20the%20coastline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20said%20that%20as%20of%20Monday%20night%2C%20it%20had%20ordered%20more%20than%2097%2C000%20people%20in%20nine%20prefectures%20on%20Honshu%20to%20evacuate.%20Authorities%20later%20downgraded%20the%20major%20tsunami%20warning%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctsunami%20advisory%2C%E2%80%9D%20but%20people%20were%20still%20urged%20to%20move%20to%20higher%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%E2%80%99s%20meteorological%20agency%20warned%20that%20a%2045-centimetre%20high%20(1.5%20feet)%20tsunami%20on%20the%20South%20Korean%20east%20coast%20can%20grow%20and%20continue%20for%20more%20than%20a%20day.%20The%20Hawaii-based%20Pacific%20Tsunami%20Warning%20Center%2C%20however%2C%20said%20later%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20tsunami%20threat%20has%20now%20largely%20passed.%E2%80%9D%20Emergency%20services%20in%20the%20far%20eastern%20Russian%20island%20of%20Sakhalin%20issued%20an%20alert%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20island%E2%80%99s%20western%20coast%20%E2%80%9Cmay%20be%20affected%20by%20tsunami%20waves.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorth%20Korea%20also%20issued%20a%20tsunami%20warning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20we%20know%20about%20the%20earthquake%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Noto%20region%20saw%20a%20rapid%20succession%20of%20earthquakes%2C%20starting%20with%20a%205.7%20magnitude%20tremor%20at%20around%204%3A06%20pm%20local%20time%20(0704%20UTC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%207.6-magnitude%20quake%20hit%20just%20four%20minutes%20later%20and%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20series%20of%20weaker%20tremors%20for%20around%2090%20minutes%2C%20said%20the%20JMA.%20In%20total%2C%20the%20agency%20recorded%2021%20quakes%20of%204.0%20magnitude%20or%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovernment%20spokesman%20Yoshimasa%20Hayashi%20said%20