also%20used%20to%20narrate%20stories%20of%20when%20the%20Japanese%20troops%20entered%20her%20village%20of%20Jakhama.%20It%20was%20a%20traumatic%20time%20in%20their%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Asalie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_357823542_1259424638023921_5888304989041501718_n_1080-1700749912.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Moko%20Koza%20with%20his%20grandmother.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_357823542_1259424638023921_5888304989041501718_n_1080-1700749912.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_357823542_1259424638023921_5888304989041501718_n_1080-1700749912-300x253.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_357823542_1259424638023921_5888304989041501718_n_1080-1700749912-500x421.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_357823542_1259424638023921_5888304989041501718_n_1080-1700749912-768x646.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FSnapinsta.app_357823542_1259424638023921_5888304989041501718_n_1080-1700749912-150x126.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334846%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22909%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMoko%20Koza%20with%20his%20grandmother.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20Moko%20does%20a%20great%20job%20of%20being%20musically%20relevant%20with%20modern%20styles%20yet%20at%20the%20same%20time%20staying%20connected%20to%20his%20roots%20with%20the%20content%20of%20his%20songs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20feature%20also%20appears%20in%20songs%20like%20%E2%80%98Tribally%20Savage%E2%80%99%20which%20was%20released%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20music%20video%2C%20Moko%20makes%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20events%20of%204%20December%2C%202021%2C%20when%20Indian%20security%20forces%20killed%2014%20innocent%20civilians%20from%20Oting%20village%20in%20Mon%20district%2C%20mistaking%20them%20for%20armed%20militants.%20He%20goes%20on%20to%20make%20a%20plea%20for%20repealing%20the%20draconian%20Armed%20Forces%20(Special%20Powers)%20Act%20(AFSPA)%2C%20which%20gives%20Indian%20security%20forces%20immunity%20to%20use%20force%20%E2%80%9Ceven%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20causing%20death%E2%80%9D.%20In%20past%20interviews%2C%20Moko%20has%20spoken%20of%20wanting%20to%20end%20this%20cycle%20of%20violence%20which%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20more%20than%20five%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20a%20long-standing%20ceasefire%20between%20the%20Indian%20state%20and%20armed%20groups%20seeking%20a%20separate%20homeland%20for%20the%20Naga%20people%2C%20core%20political%20disputes%20stand%20unresolved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FrZMvfTjq9pI%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FrZMvfTjq9pI%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%